{"tid":988622,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Switch] 八方旅人 Octopath Traveler 集中討論區 (4)","createTime":"2019-01-20T08:37:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T12:41:36.000Z","uid":12351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e853966b2f8c52a508c40132859a371b8cd5bad2","tid":988622,"uid":12351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:37:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/711inMoRQVL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-na.ssl-images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F711inMoRQVL.jpg&h=ff40a6c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《八方旅人》（日語：オクトパス トラベラー，英語：Octopath Traveler）是由史克威爾艾尼克斯和Acquire開發的電子角色扮演遊戲，預定於2018年7月13日在任天堂Switch平台發售。遊戲使用魔域幻境引擎4開發，畫面採用結合復古像素點陣與3DCG的風格，官方稱該風格為「HD-2D」。遊戲的故事發生在奧魯斯特拉（オルステラ）大陸，玩家需要扮演出身迥異，各懷絕技而又各有所求的八名旅人中其中一人，踏上他/她的旅途。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n角色預告片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jCaXSxYrrWM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjCaXSxYrrWM&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=f72c9f11\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jCaXSxYrrWM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<del>香港官方網站：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/octopath_traveler/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nintendo.com.hk%2Fswitch%2Foctopath_traveler%2F&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=b612df43\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nintendo.com.hk/switch/octopath_traveler/</a></del><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本官方網站：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.jp.square-enix.com/octopathtraveler/sp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jp.square-enix.com%2Foctopathtraveler%2Fsp%2F&d=HiUNBysZrE9nbvaLZxqmO4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=267c16f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.jp.square-enix.com/octopathtraveler/sp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">常見問題</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\nQ: 有無<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">中文</span></strong>?<br />\nA: 截至出post一刻未有官方消息。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 咁<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">行日美歐版</span></strong>嘅分別係?<br />\nA: 遊戲內容係無分別，全部都包含所有語言，但係如果要繼承<span style=\"color: red;\">demo</span>進度就要買返同demo一樣嘅版本啦<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點樣<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">轉遊戲語言</span></strong>做「日文」或「英文」?<br />\nA: 起Switch系統設定入面將系統語言轉做相應語言<br />\n<br />\nQ: 接左啲<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>支線任務</strong></span>去邊度睇返? 有無<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>提示</strong></span>點解任務?<br />\nA: X掣 -&gt; Journal -&gt; R掣。 大部分支線都有<span style=\"color: red;\">幾種</span>解任方法，遊戲內無直接提示，如果要我俾個提示你的話我會話: <span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">善用角色技能</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>一開始揀個角色</strong></span>重唔重要?<br />\nA: 第一個角色要全破佢劇情後先可移出隊伍，所以最好揀個鍾意嘅。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 有啲<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>角色技能(Path Action) </strong></span>效果差唔多，其實有咩<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">分別</span></strong>?<br />\nA: 主要係分正道同邪道: 一個有等級限制; 一個唔限lv 但失敗會扣聲望值<br />\n<img src=\"https://s26.postimg.cc/3txkqoegp/161342_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.cc%2F3txkqoegp%2F161342_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=e1f57146&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nQ: 有時會撞到隻<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>貓(Cait)</strong></span>, 打唔入又易逃走, 係咩來同點打?<br />\nA: 係肥料來架，打完收獲豐富。建議用<span style=\"color: red;\">魔法</span>打，因為魔法唔會Miss。由於evasion值高，建議用多次連擊武器打佢。順帶一提舞女招奇異恩典(Bewildering Grace) 有機會加經，如果咁好彩出到加經就fat fat啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ: 睇敵人嘅<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>Break弱點</strong></span>有咩技巧?<br />\nA: <img src=\"https://s26.postimg.cc/u28pg1quh/p4p62dylmta11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs26.postimg.cc%2Fu28pg1quh%2Fp4p62dylmta11.png&h=92b11c56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n必定係跟上圖順序排，所以如果見到左起第二弱點係槍，第一問號一定係劍<br />\n<br />\nQ: <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>寶箱</strong></span>見到掂唔到要點算?<br />\nA: 鎖左嘅紫金箱要賊仔先開到。如果係見到但無路去到嘅... 周圍再細心揾下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQ: 點開<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>第二職業</strong></span>?<br />\nA: 地圖上有啲好特別嘅野，入去「過左關」就開到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a0378179e63ad7a378d86b658a250724ba78b0","tid":988622,"uid":12351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T08:42:45.000Z","msg":"近排玩翻有野問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家接近end game 拎哂上位職 本身Cyrus副神官但宜家做左魔法師 諗唔到神官俾邊個好 就咁用Alfyn做另一隊嘅補師夠唔夠用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79518ac5afdf69d074657f78de95c4f1a6fdace","tid":988622,"uid":36509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"《OCTOPATH TRAVELER》中文化決定！中文譯名為《OCTOPATH TRAVELER 歧路旅人》，預定於6月7日10AM (香港時間)發佈。"},{"pid":"6ed24592e00fd21144320df64f53ba075471597d","tid":988622,"uid":198992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a79518ac5afdf69d074657f78de95c4f1a6fdace","tid":988622,"uid":36509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"《OCTOPATH TRAVELER》中文化決定！中文譯名為《OCTOPATH TRAVELER 歧路旅人》，預定於6月7日10AM (香港時間)發佈。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"好耐冇玩 淨係爆左一個主角 而家終於可以慢慢睇故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dd276b8aa4f71fb0f6c05d30f8d678091a43df","tid":988622,"uid":77769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:03:32.000Z","msg":"steam版6月8號先有得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd04913ec93f76a53a1be72fc27a12d975d5ed85","tid":988622,"ui